Hortonworks HDP cluster deployment

CFEngine version: 3.6.6

1. Provide (install and configure) next software:
               yum,rpm,scp,curl,unzip,tar,wget,openssl
               python v2.6 (For RHEL6.X or CentOS6.X) and python v2.7 (not later than 2.7.8 for RHEL6.X or CentOS6.X)
2. Set passwordless SSH
3. Configure ntp, network, selinux, iptables, system settings
4. Install JDK.
5. Configure and start Ambari server and agents
6. Install, configure and deploy a HDP cluster by blueprints
